### Content Moderation API Tests

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/health

### 2. Test API Key (Check if Cohere API key is working)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/test-api-key

### 3. Test Entries (Test with specific content types)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/test-entries

### 4. Debug Test (Run this first to check if moderation is working)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/debug-test

### 5. Simple Content Moderation - Safe Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/moderate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Beautiful handmade wooden table for sale. Perfect for living room decoration."
}

### 6. Simple Content Moderation - Unsafe Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/moderate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "This product contains explicit adult content and violence."
}

### 7. Detailed Content Moderation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/moderate-detailed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "This product contains explicit adult content and violence."
}

### 8. Product Moderation - Safe Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/moderate-product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Handmade Wooden Coffee Table",
  "description": "Beautiful handcrafted coffee table made from premium oak wood. Perfect for living room decoration.",
  "sellerId": "user123"
}

### 9. Product Moderation - Unsafe Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/moderate-product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Explicit Adult Content",
  "description": "This product contains explicit sexual content and adult material that is inappropriate.",
  "sellerId": "user789"
}

### 10. Batch Moderation (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ContentModeration/moderate-batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "texts": [
    "Handmade jewelry collection",
    "Professional photography services",
    "Explicit adult content here",
    "Beautiful ceramic vase"
  ]
}

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@adminToken = your_admin_jwt_token_here 